    'description' => 'Generate a PNG bar chart image from numeric data using PHP\'s GD library. Takes arrays of labels and values, creates a professionally styled bar chart with axes, gridlines, and labels. Outputs a PNG file to the workspace. First tool in the ecosystem to CREATE an image from scratch (all others only analyze or download existing images). Never throws — all errors returned as structured data.',
    'parameters' => 
